Dialogs.Dialog: Do you want to go to another place？
Hey, hey, isn't it time to start our date？
Hey, should we go to our date spot？
Yeah, this looks nice. Let's go.
...What's wrong？ Don't you want to go？
Did I arrive here first？ Did I beat you？
...Our date has almost run out of time.
Yes, it's time to go home.
I don't want to say it... But, look at the clock.
Ah, it's late. We have to go back home.
I see. I guess we can't do anything now.
Is it almost the end of the day？
Yeah, we have to go back home.
I see. It's time to go home.
I want to stay a little longer, but I have to go home.
Sorry, it's time to go home.
Any more, and Papa will get angry.
Oh no, we ran out of time！
I'm looking forward for where you'll take me.
Want to pick where to go next？
I want you to take me to a funny place.
I get lost easily. Hey, where do you want to go？
Do you want to choose where to go ▲主人公＊▲？
Haven't you decided where we should go？
Yes. I don't want you to go...
This is getting fun. What do you want to do next？
It was fun. What are we doing next？
I knew it, it was more fun together. What do you want to do after this？
Is it time to change places？
What should we do after this？
Okay, let's go to another place.
Hey, do you want to go here？
Well, right here is... Do you want me to say it？
Which movie is good... Do you have any recommendations？
Hey, which one do you recommend？ Want to go？
What do you want to watch？ I'll go with you.
Emm... I can't decide. Baton pass.
Which one do you want to see？
It's alright, please choose what'd you like.
Do you still have time？ I was wondering if we could watch another.
It was really good. I'm also interested in others movies as well.
I see. Do you want to watch another one？
I have a suggestion. Want to do a movie day today？
I'm not worrying about anything else. Why don't we just watch another one？
I want to see another one. I hope you still have some time.
Of course, I feel like watching other...
I feel like it's not enough. Do you want to watch another movie？
Yeah, I felt it too. What do you want to watch？
Hehe, we're matching. I like that too.
Yeah. Do you want to go there？
I wonder if that place it's fun.
Right there？ ...Yeah, you won't know unless you go.
Hey, do you know of a good place around here for lunch？
Oh, your timing was good. I was getting hungry.
It's about lunch time... Ah, I'm hungry... Well, just a little.
Hey, are you hungry？ I might feel a bit peckish.
Is that time already？ Okay, let's go have some lunch.
Ah, it's almost lunch time. Let's go grab some food.
Hey, didn't you forget about something？ It's time.
Ah, it's lunch time. I'm sorry, let's go.
Aren't you thirsty？ Let's take a break around here and have some tea.
Oh, that sounds nice. Let's go.
I want to take our time while we're talking...
Do you want to have some tea？
Hey, why don't we take a break while having some tea？
Sorry, my legs are getting a little tired.
Do you want to have a break with some tea？
I want to take a break. Can we rest a little？
Can I have dinner with you tonight？
It's almost time to eat... I want to eat together.
We'll have dinner together after this... right？
Hey, aren't you feeling a bit hungry？ I'm a little hungry.
Me too. Then, let's go somewhere to eat.
It's about time to eat. I'm feeling a little hungry. What about you？
Me too. Let's decide where to eat.
I still have time to eat before going home.
Alright, next time let's have dinner together.
We arrived. Hurry up, hurry up！
We arrived. Have you decided what to order first？
I'm so hungry. Everything looks so delicious.
Should I try a different menu？
I said I might be late today...
Are you really going back home？ Don't you want to be with me a little more？
More... I want to be with you more. Can't I？
Yes, I also want to be with you.
I don't want to go home yet...
Me neither. Let's continue our date.
Can we continue with our date？
Of course. I'll follow you anywhere.
Okay, let's have some more fun.
I still have some free time. If its okay to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Thank you, let's play a little more.
I wonder where should we go...
It's getting late, let's go home.
Yup, no objection whatsoever... I'm kidding.
We're going to far now, at this hour...
I'm sorry, I didn't think about the distance.
Hey, that takes some time to reach.
You're right, we might be late.
If you want to go that far, maybe I should try doing my best too.
Oh, you're right. It's a little too far.
Over there... I'm sorry, but I think we should head home.
Hmm. I'm sorry, I think we shouldn't go that far.
...I understand. Let's head back home for today...
